      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under an institutional license with documented version control. The solver has an established regression test suite covering laminar and turbulent internal flow benchmarks. Release notes and known-issue logs are maintained. SQA level is consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device submission."
