      "rationale": "Code verification was confirmed against the lid-driven cavity benchmark (Re = 1000) and a Poiseuille flow channel case. Observed order of accuracy matched theoretical second-order convergence for the pressure-velocity coupling scheme. No code defects were identified relevant to the pump hemolysis application."
