      "rationale": "Inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid temperature, and hematocrit for the in-vitro hemolysis experiments are documented in the project technical file. Boundary conditions in the CFD model were matched to measured experimental values within stated measurement uncertainty. Temperature was controlled to 37 ± 0.5°C in both experiment and simulation."
    },
    {
