      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted NIH values must agree with experimental measurements within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty at each operating point.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions were compared to in-vitro measurements at three of five operating points where experimental data were available. Mean absolute error was 8.3% relative to experimental NIH, within the combined uncertainty band of ±12%. At the two operating points lacking experimental data, predictions were bracketed by interpolation from adjacent validated points. The output comparison supports the credibility of the hemolysis model for the CPB COU."
    },
    {
